State 0

    0 $accept: • script $end

    OPTION  shift, and go to state 1

    $default  reduce using rule 2 (opt_options)

    script       go to state 2
    opt_options  go to state 3
    options      go to state 4
    option       go to state 5
    option_flag  go to state 6


State 1

    7 option_flag: OPTION •

    $default  reduce using rule 7 (option_flag)


State 2

    0 $accept: script • $end

    $end  shift, and go to state 7


State 3

    1 script: opt_options • events

    MYFLOAT  shift, and go to state 8
    INTEGER  shift, and go to state 9
    '+'      shift, and go to state 10
    '*'      shift, and go to state 11

    events      go to state 12
    event       go to state 13
    event_time  go to state 14
    time        go to state 15


State 4

    3 opt_options: options •
    5 options: options • option

    OPTION  shift, and go to state 1

    $default  reduce using rule 3 (opt_options)

    option       go to state 16
    option_flag  go to state 6


State 5

    4 options: option •

    $default  reduce using rule 4 (options)


State 6

    6 option: option_flag • '=' option_value

    '='  shift, and go to state 17


State 7

    0 $accept: script $end •

    $default  accept


State 8

   19 time: MYFLOAT •

    $default  reduce using rule 19 (time)


State 9

   20 time: INTEGER •

    $default  reduce using rule 20 (time)


State 10

   14 event_time: '+' • time
   18           | '+' • time '~' '+' time

    MYFLOAT  shift, and go to state 8
    INTEGER  shift, and go to state 9

    time  go to state 18


State 11

   16 event_time: '*' •

    $default  reduce using rule 16 (event_time)


State 12

    1 script: opt_options events •
   12 events: events • event

    MYFLOAT  shift, and go to state 8
